        "description": "StartFragment\n\n# Create Plan\n\nCreates a new recharge plan associated with a specific operator. Each plan must be linked to a valid operator using `operatorId`.\n\n---\n\n## Endpoint Details\n\n| Property | Value |\n| --- | --- |\n| Method | POST |\n| URL | [http://localhost:8086/aperatormanagement/plans/create](http://localhost:8086/aperatormanagement/plans/create) |\n| Content-Type | application/json |\n\n---\n\n## Request Body Parameters\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n| amount | number | Price of the recharge plan |\n| validity | string | Validity period (e.g., 28 days) |\n| description | string | Details of the plan (e.g., data, calls) |\n| operatorId | long | ID of the operator to which this plan belongs |\n\n---\n\n## Sample Request Body\n\n```\n{\n  \"amount\": 199,\n  \"validity\": \"28 days\",\n  \"description\": \"1.5GB/day\",\n  \"operatorId\": 1\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## Response\n\n### ✅ Success — 200 OK\n\n```\n{\n  \"amount\": 199,\n  \"validity\": \"28 days\",\n  \"description\": \"1.5GB/day\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Notes\n\n- `operatorId` must exist in the system\n    \n- Always create operator before creating a plan"
